            End of Twitter post  by @Acosta
        
    

How did the row begin?During the 8 November news conference, a White House intern tried to take the microphone from Mr Acosta as he attempted to ask the president a follow-up question.Mr Trump called Acosta "a rude, terrible person" and the reporter was barred from entering the White House a day later.CNN filed a lawsuit to have Acosta's pass restored, and was joined by other media organisations in their efforts including conservative-leaning Fox News.
                
                
                
                
                
